<table border=0 cellspacing=1 cellpadding=1>
	<tr>
		<td valign=middle align=left width=22><IMG src="/help/images/clear.gif" height=1 width=20 border=0></td>
		<td valign=middle align=right class="header">Managing Folders</td>
	</tr>
	<tr><td valign=top align=left colspan="2"><hr size="1"></td></tr>
	<tr><td valign=top align=left colspan="2" class="text">Folders can be created to manage messages efficiently.</td></tr>
	<tr><td valign=top align=left colspan="2" class="text"><IMG src="/help/images/clear.gif" height=5 width=1 border=0></td></tr>
	<tr><td valign=top align=left colspan="2" class="subheader">Create New folder</td></tr>
    <tr>
		<td valign=top align=left width=22 class="text">1.</td>
		
    <td valign=top align=left class="text">To create a new folder, click on the 
      <strong>Options > Manage Folders</strong> link.</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td valign=top align=left width=22 class="text">2.</td>
		
    <td valign=top align=left class="text">All folders created will be listed 
      with a disk usage indication, click on the <strong>New Folder</strong> button.</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td valign=top align=left width=22 class="text">3.</td>
		
    <td valign=top align=left class="text">Enter the <em>Folder Name</em> and 
      select the appropriate <em>Parent Folder</em> if it is a sub-folder.</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td valign=top align=left width=22 class="text">4.</td>
		
    <td valign=top align=left class="text">Lastly, click on the <strong>Submit</strong> 
      button to save.</td>
	</tr>
	<tr><td valign=top align=left colspan="2" class="text"><IMG src="/help/images/clear.gif" height=5 width=1 border=0></td></tr>
	<tr><td valign=top align=left colspan="2" class="subheader">Edit Folder</td></tr>
    <tr>
		<td valign=top align=left width=22 class="text">1.</td>
		
    <td valign=top align=left class="text">To edit an existing folder, click on 
      the <strong>Options > Manage Folders </strong>link.</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td valign=top align=left width=22 class="text">2.</td>
		
    <td valign=top align=left class="text">Click on the <em>Folder Name</em> to 
      change the details of the folder.</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td valign=top align=left width=22 class="text">3.</td>
		
    <td valign=top align=left class="text">Change the <em>Folder Name</em> and 
      <em>Parent Folder.</em></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td valign=top align=left width=22 class="text">4.</td>
		
    <td valign=top align=left class="text">Click on the <strong>Submit</strong> 
      button to save the changes.</td>
	</tr>
	<tr><td valign=top align=left colspan="2" class="text"><IMG src="/help/images/clear.gif" height=5 width=1 border=0></td></tr>
	<tr><td valign=top align=left colspan="2" class="subheader">Delete Folder</td></tr>
    <tr>
		<td valign=top align=left width=22 class="text">1.</td>
		
    <td valign=top align=left class="text">To delete an existing folder, click 
      on the <strong>Options > Manage Folders </strong>link.</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td valign=top align=left width=22 class="text">2.</td>
		
    <td valign=top align=left class="text">Put a tick in the checkbox at the folders 
      that you wish to delete.</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td valign=top align=left width=22 class="text">3.</td>
		
    <td valign=top align=left class="text">Click on the <strong>Delete </strong>button. 
      A pop-up confirmation message will appear before the folder is deleted. 
      Click on the <strong>OK</strong> button to delete or on the <strong>Cancel</strong> 
      button to cancel.</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td valign=top align=left width=22 class="text">4.</td>
		
    <td valign=top align=left class="text">Caution: Deleting a folder will cause 
      all its subfolders and messages to be deleted as well.</td>
	</tr>
</table>
